rian%20communities%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections.%20It%20also%20serves%20the%20purpose%20of%20raking%20up%20the%20periods%20of%20anti-Congress%20past%20of%20these%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20Modi%20had%20%E2%80%9Cfulfilled%20the%20dream%20of%20Chaudhary%20Ajit%20Singh%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20late%20father%20who%2C%20incidentally%2C%20had%20allied%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20past%20on%20more%20than%20one%20occasion.%20The%202013%20Muzaffarnagar%20communal%20violence%20and%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20that%20followed%20it%2C%20drastically%20changed%20the%20game%20in%20west%20UP%2C%20scripting%20the%20downfall%20of%20the%20RLD%20and%20the%20sudden%20and%20steep%20rise%20of%20the%20BJP%20as%20the%20dominant%20force%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20praising%20Modi%20for%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20for%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Jayant%20also%20spoke%20a%20new%20language%2C%20using%20phrases%20one%20often%20hears%20from%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%20He%20said%20no%20other%20government%20in%20the%20past%20could%20honour%20Charan%20Singh%20with%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%20but%20it%20had%20become%20possible%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfearless%E2%80%9D%20manner%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9CModi%E2%80%99s%20vision%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Csense%20of%20commitment%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cefforts.%E2%80%9D%20It%20would%20be%20remembered%20by%20generations%20to%20come%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20only%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20people%20in%20the%20mainstream%20took%20decisions%2C%20added%20Jayant%2C%20in%20an%20apparent%20dig%20at%20previous%20Congress%20governments%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20conferring%20the%20honours%20on%20Charan%20Singh.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20New%20Bharat%2C%20things%20are%20changing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoll%20calculations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20speculation%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20made%20an%20offer%20of%20some%20seats%20to%20the%20RLD%20in%20west%20UP%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20ministerial%20berth%20or%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20PM%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20announced%20that%20Charan%20Singh%20was%20being%20conferred%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20in%20the%20country.%20Modi%20hailed%20Charan%20Singh%20for%20his%20role%20in%20%E2%80%9Cnation%20building%E2%80%9D%20and%20dedicating%20his%20life%20to%20the%20rights%20and%20welfare%20of%20farmers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20%E2%80%9Ccommitment%20to%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20Emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RLD%20has%20nine%20MLAs%20in%20UP%20including%20two%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20party%20made%20an%20immense%20gain%20in%20seat%20and%20vote%20share%20as%20it%20fought%20the%20election%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP.%20In%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20if%20Jayant%20does%20make%20the%20big%20jump%20to%20NDA%2C%20he%20is%20bound%20to%20face%20some%20uncomfortable%20questions%20as%20he%20has%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years%20been%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20and%20often%20accused%20it%20of%20fanning%20communal%20politics%20and%20working%20against%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20farmers.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fagnipath-military-recruitment-scheme-questions-efficacy-remain%5C%22%3EJayant%20had%20opposed%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20Agniveer%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20criticised%20the%20state%20government%20run%20by%20the%20BJP%20for%20not%20providing%20sugarcane%20farmers%20with%20the%20right%20minimum%20support%20price%20and%20mobilised%20Jats%20and%20Muslims%20to%20build%20a%20brotherhood%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20communally%20divide%20and%20polarise%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20already%20seems%20to%20be%20prepared%20with%20a%20narrative.%20When%20asked%20by%20journalists%20if%20he%20would%20continue%20to%20oppose%20the%20government%20and%20join%20the%20upcoming%20farmers%20protests%2C%20Jayant%20turned%20diplomatic.%20He%20said%20no%20government%20could%20provide%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpermanent%20solution%E2%80%9D%20to%20grievances%20of%20people%20and%20that%20it%20would%20always%20include%20%E2%80%9Ccontinuous%20efforts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Csentiment%2C%20dedication%20and%20will%20power%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20displayed%20towards%20the%20rural%20and%20working-class%20people%20by%20conferring%20Charan%20Singh%20with%20Bharat%20Ratna%20provided%20courage%20to%20these%20people%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20Charan%20Singh%20would%20also%20be%20heard%2C%20said%20Jayant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOld%20comments%2C%20new%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RLD%20chief%20might%20also%20have%20to%20encounter%20uncomfortable%20questions%20about%20a%20statement%20he%20had%20made%20in%20the%20heat%20of%20the%202022%20UP%20assembly%20election%2C%20when%20he%20had%20rejected%20an%20offer%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20join%20the%20saffron%20alliance.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20a%20%3Cem%3Echavanni%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20will%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jayant%20had%20said%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20while%20asking%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20SP-RLD%20combine%20against%20the%20BJP.%20A%20%E2%80%98chavanni%E2%80%99%20is%20a%2025%20paise%20coin%2C%20but%20it%20is%20also%20a%20derogatory%20way%20to%20say%20that%20something%20is%20valueless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20journalists%20pointed%20this%20out%20to%20him%20on%20Friday%2C%20Jayant%20said%20he%20would%20not%20delete%20any%20of%20his%20old%20tweets.%20He%20said%20whenever%20he%20said%20something%2C%20it%20was%20based%20on%20his%20conviction%20during%20that%20moment.%20On%20January%2019%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20RLD%20and%20the%20SP%20confirmed%20a%20tie-up%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20Jayant%20had%20posted%20on%20X%20that%20the%20alliance%20was%20%E2%80%9Calways%20ready%20to%20protect%20national%20and%20constitutional%20values.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20SP%20chief%20Yadav%20was%20asked%20by%20reporters%20in%20Lucknow%20if%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20Jayant%2C%20he%20said%20there%20had%20been%20no%20recent%20talks%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20UP%20assembly%2C%20however%2C%20Yadav%20congratulated%20all%20farmers%20for%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20Charan%20Singh.%20Yadav%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20was%20his%20father%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20who%20had%20installed%20a%20statue%20of%20Charan%20Singh%20in%20front%20of%20the%20UP%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20RLD%20contested%20three%20seats%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20including%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party.%20But%20it%20lost%20all%20three%20seats.%20While%20Jayant%20lost%20in%20Baghpat%2C%20his%20father%20Ajit%20Singh%20too%20failed%20in%20Muzaffarnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RLD%E2%80%99s%20shift%20to%20the%20saffron%20alliance%20will%20definitely%20change%20the%20social%20equations%20in%20the%20region%20as%20the%20party%20banks%20heavily%20on%20the%20support%20of%20Jats%20and%20Muslims.%20The%20minority%20community%20is%20unlikely%20to%20maintain%20its%20support%20to%20the%20RLD%20in%20case%20it%20contests%20in%20a%20pre-poll%20with%20the%20BJP.%20In%20West%20UP%2C%20especially%20in%20pockets%20where%20the%20RLD%20is%20strong%2C%20Muslims%20are%20a%20substantial%20voting%20segment%2C%20much%20above%20the%20state%20average%20of%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20this%20means%20is%20that%20while%20it%20opens%20doors%20for%20the%20BSP%20to%20attract%20Muslim%20voters%20on%20some%20seats%2C%20it%20also%20makes%20the%20SP%20and%20Congress%20the%20main%20Opposition%20bloc%20in%20the%20state%20which%20sends%2080%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20Congress%20could%20get%20a%20better%20share%20in%20its%20seat-sharing%20deal%20with%20the%20SP%20which%20has%20so%20far%20only%20confirmed%2011%20seats%20for%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20as%20part%20of%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20the%20RLD%20would%20ensure%20a%20higher%20possibility%20of%20Hindu%20consolidation%20in%20west%20UP%2C%20where%20it%20was%20already%20strong%20and%20secured%20votes%20on%20average%20above%2050%25%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RLD%E2%80%99s%20shift%20would%20also%20have%20immediate%20repercussions%20on%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20as%20the%20party%20has%20nine%20MLAs%20and%20could%20spoil%20the%20arithmetic%20for%20the%20SP.%20With%20108%20seats%2C%20the%20SP%20would%20have%20no%20formal%20allies%20left%20in%20the%20UP%20Assembly.%20The%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar-led%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20already%20exited%20the%20SP-led%20alliance%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saffron%20party%20has%20three%20OBC%20allies%20in%20East%20UP%20%E2%80%93%20the%20SBSP%2C%20Nishad%20Party%20and%20Apna%20Dal%20(Soneylal).%20With%20the%20entry%20of%20the%20RLD%2C%20it%20would%20gain%20a%20strong%20regional%20partner%20in%20west%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RLD%20has%20four%20MLA%20seats%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20two%20in%20Shamli%2C%20one%20each%20in%20Meerut%2C%20Hathras%20and%20Baghpat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayant%20Singh%20is%20its%20sole%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member.%20More%20clarity%20is%20expected%20on%20the%20RLD%E2%80%99s%20future%20on%20February%2012%2C%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Ajit%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707483648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09183000%2FScreenshot-2024-02-09-at-6.26.27.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchaudhary-charan-singh-bharat-ratna-jayant-rld-nda-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20grandson%20of%20posthumous%20Bharat%20Ratna%20recipient%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Jayant%20did%20not%20once%20deny%20that%20he%20w