an-rs-570-crore-sold-in-january-alone-60-in-the-value-of-rs-1-crore%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Curry%20on%20Regardless%3A%20Culinary%20Conflicts%20That%20Take%20the%20Cake%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09134240%2FThe_best_Butter_Chicken.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20came%20first%2C%20the%20chicken%20or%20the%20ego%3F%20That%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20lawsuit%20that%E2%80%99s%20cooking%20up%20a%20storm%20in%20a%20Delhi%20court%2C%20concerning%20the%20provenance%20of%20a%20curry%20preparation%20consisting%20of%20pieces%20of%20poultry%20smothered%20in%20thick%20tomato%20gravy%2C%20enriched%20with%20lashings%20of%20butter%2C%20which%20is%20known%20and%20relished%20not%20only%20all%20over%20the%20country%20but%20also%20in%20foreign%20fields%20forever%20%3Cem%3Edesi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20great%20Indian%20diaspora%2C%20and%20known%20as%20butter%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20renowned%20Delhi%20restaurants%20are%20engaged%20in%20a%20legal%20kitchen-sink%20drama%20to%20establish%20who%20is%20the%20true%20begetter%20of%20the%20dish%2C%20with%20each%20accusing%20the%20other%20of%20copy-cattery%20most%20fowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChroniclers%20of%20cuisine%20trace%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20disputed%20dish%20to%20pre-Partition%20Peshawar%20when%20a%20young%20man%20called%20Mokha%20Singh%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20three%20partners%2C%20started%20an%20eatery%20called%20Moti%20Mahal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Partition%2C%20Singh%20found%20himself%20in%20Delhi%20where%20he%20chanced%20upon%20his%20former%20associates%2C%20who%20convinced%20him%20to%20relaunch%20their%20joint-venture%20restaurant%20in%20Daryaganj%20where%2C%20according%20to%20foodie%20lore%2C%20butter%20chicken%20was%20hatched%20by%20happy%20happenstance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrift%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20improvisation%2C%20inspired%20the%20entrepreneurs%20to%20douse%20left-over%20tikkas%20with%20tomato%20gravy%2C%20creamed%20with%20dollops%20of%20butter%20and%20%E2%80%93%20before%20you%20could%20say%20Eureka!%20in%20Punjabi%20%E2%80%93%20culinary%20history%20was%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Butter%20Chicken%20the%20speciality%20of%20the%20house%2C%20the%20new%20Moti%20Mahal%20gained%20an%20enthusiastic%20patronage%20which%20reportedly%20included%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201984%2C%20a%3Cem%3E%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20quoted%20Indian%20independence%20activist%20Maulana%20Azad%20recommending%20to%20the%20Shah%20of%20Iran%20that%20on%20his%20trip%20to%20India%20he%20%E2%80%9Cmust%20make%20two%20visits%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20and%20to%20Moti%20Mahal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenown%2C%20however%2C%20often%20goes%20before%20rivalry%2C%20and%20descendants%20of%20the%20original%20establishment%20started%20a%20competing%20restaurant%20which%20claimed%20proprietorial%20rights%20over%20the%20original%20butter%20chicken%2C%20a%20contention%20now%20up%20for%20hearing%20to%20determine%20who%E2%80%99s%20making%20a%20%3Cem%3Emurga%3C%2Fem%3E%20out%20of%20whom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Fthe-wire-recommends-the-meals-we-remember-from-2023%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%20Recommends%3A%20The%20Meals%20We%20Remember%20From%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20chickens%20that%20come%20to%20roost%20in%20courts%2C%20which%20are%20also%20approached%20by%20those%20who%20feel%20that%20they%E2%80%99ve%20not%20got%20their%20just%20deserts%2C%20or%20desserts.%20In%202015%2C%20Bengal%20and%20Odisha%20locked%20horns%20over%20who%20could%20rightly%20lay%20claim%20to%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Erasagulla%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20get%20geographical%20indication%20(GI)%20for%20the%20succulent%20confection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdisha%20refuted%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20that%20the%20sweet%20was%20created%20in%20Calcutta%20by%20Nobin%20Chandra%20Das%20in%201868%2C%20and%20predated%20the%20Odisha%20version.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20Odisha%20said%2C%20the%20rasagulla%20saw%20the%20light%20of%20day%20in%20Puri%20in%20the%2012th%20century%20as%20a%20votive%20offering%20in%20the%20Jagannath%20temple.%20The%20state%20government%20declared%20July%2030%20as%20%3Cem%3ERasagulla%20Dibasa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Rasagulla%20Day).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Bengal%20announced%20that%20henceforth%20December%2028%20would%20be%20observed%20as%3Cem%3E%20Rossogolla%20Utsob%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Rasagulla%20Festival).every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20courtroom%20tussle%20over%20the%20sweetmeat%20lasted%20over%20two%20years%20and%20concluded%20with%20both%20sides%20claiming%20separate%20GI%20status%20of%20their%20version%20of%20the%20delicacy%20%E2%80%93%20a%20gratifying%20conclusion%20for%20those%20who%20profess%20to%20have%20a%20sweet%20tooth%20as%20well%20as%20a%20penchant%20for%20the%20sweet%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20confected%20cause%20c%C3%A9l%C3%A8bre%2C%20which%20literally%20takes%20the%20cake%2C%20Vienna%20became%20an%20arena%20for%20food%20feud%20over%20a%20dessert%20which%20traces%20its%20origin%20to%201832%2C%20the%20famous%20Sacher%20Torte.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20torte%20was%20conceived%20when%20the%20pastry%20chef%20of%20Clemens%2C%20Wenzel%20Lothar%20Furst%20von%20Metternich%2C%20fell%20ill%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20a%20dinner%20party%20and%20a%2016-year-old%20apprentice%2C%20Franz%20Sacher%2C%20had%20to%20be%20roped%20in%20to%20fit%20the%20bill%20of%20fare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFranz%20came%20up%20with%20a%20chocolate%20gateau%20with%20two%20layers%20of%20apricot%20jam%2C%20a%20recipe%20which%20he%20subsequently%20perfected%20over%2012%20years%20in%20his%20family-owned%20Sacher%20Hotel%2C%20and%20which%20was%20kept%20under%20a%20wrap%20of%20secrecy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFranz%E2%80%99s%20eldest%20son%2C%20Eduard%2C%20having%20completed%20his%20own%20apprenticeship%20at%20Vienna%E2%80%99s%20Demel%20Bakery%2C%20which%20catered%20to%20Austria%E2%80%99s%20royal%20family%2C%20joined%20his%20family%20enterprise.%20Some%20years%20later%20however%2C%20financial%20compulsion%20made%20him%20grant%20Demel%20Bakery%20the%20sole%20rights%20to%20market%20the%20%E2%80%98Eduard%20Sacher%20Torte%E2%80%99%2C%20even%20as%20the%20Sacher%20Hotel%20continued%20to%20sell%20the%20%E2%80%98Original%20Sacher%20Torte%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20resulted%20in%20a%20legal%20tug-of-war%20that%20lasted%2030%20years.%20It%20involved%20forensic%20minutiae%20like%20how%20much%20apricot%20jam%20was%20to%20be%20found%20in%20the%20authentic%20product%20and%20whether%20it%20was%20added%20before%20or%20after%20baking%20the%20cake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20a%20compromise%20settlement%20was%20reached%20by%20allowing%20both%20brands%20to%20be%20marketed%2C%20giving%20connoisseurs%20much%20cause%20for%20debate%20as%20to%20which%20is%20the%20real%20McCoy%2C%20or%20the%20real%20McCake%2C%20and%20providing%20other%20food%20for%20torte.%20As%20well%20as%20tort.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EJug%20Suraiya%20is%20a%20well-known%20columnist%20and%20writer.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22message-text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22block-kit-renderer%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to