0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20mentally%20well%2C%20but%20finds%20it%20difficult%20to%20move%E2%80%A6his%20return%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20out%20of%20the%20question%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20quoted%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20also%20said%20that%20Singh%20told%20his%20Congress%20party%20he%20wished%20to%20quit%20his%20Rajya%20Sabha%20membership%20around%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSingh%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20point%20continuing%20if%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20discharge%20his%20duties%20fully%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20person%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20last%20few%20appearances%20in%20parliament%2C%20Singh%20was%20seen%20using%20a%20wheelchair%20for%20mobility.%20According%20to%20his%20profile%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2Frs%2Fmembers%5C%22%3ERajya%20Sabha%E2%80%99s%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20last%20attended%20parliament%20on%20December%205%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20latest%20stint%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20began%20as%20an%20MP%20for%20Rajasthan%20in%20August%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Rajya%20Sabha%20legislators%20have%20a%20term%20of%20six%20years%2C%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20ends%20in%20April%20this%20year%20as%20he%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmanmohan-singh-takes-oath-as-rajya-sabha-member-from-rajasthan-5929632%2F%5C%22%3Eserving%20the%20remainder%20of%20a%20term%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Madan%20Lal%20Saini%2C%20who%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20seat%20in%20March%202018%20but%20died%20in%20June%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20first%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20as%20an%20Assam%20MP%20in%201991.%20He%20continued%20to%20represent%20the%20state%20till%20Jun