%9Chonest%20to%20the%20core%E2%80%9D%20and%20claimed%20he%20was%20defamed%20for%20wrongdoing%20by%20others%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Frajya-sabha-bids-farewell-to-ex-prime-minister-manmohan-singh-after-33-years-in-house%2Fcid%2F1999249%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%2C%20Singh%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20saying%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20attend%20a%20dinner%20for%20retiring%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20was%20prime%20minister%2C%20Singh%20was%20also%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Union%20finance%20minister%2C%20the%20deputy%20chairman%20of%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20and%20the%20governor%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India.%20He%20also%20worked%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%20Secretariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20oversaw%20the%20liberalisation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20as%20finance%20minister%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Singh%20has%20been%20described%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Caccidental%20prime%20minister%E2%80%9D%2C%20Karan%20Thapar%20had%20interviewed%20him%20in%201999%20for%20the%20BBC%2C%20terming%20him%20then%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20likely%20candidate%20to%20be%20prime%20minister%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7inVRiqL-RQ%3Fsi%3DSMVUNdBFoofITc7v%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707468804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09142140%2FMMS.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanmohan-singh-likely-retire-public-life-far