%20They%20were%20specifically%20asked%20not%20to%20give%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20to%20those%20vehicles%20which%20had%20farmers%E2%80%99%20union%20flags%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20also%20issued%20notices%20to%20around%2020%20leaders%20of%20the%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20in%20Ambala%20district.%20A%20farmers%E2%80%99%20union%20leader%2C%20who%20too%20was%20issued%20a%20notice%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20had%20even%20asked%20them%20to%20furnish%20details%20about%20their%20bank%20accounts%20before%20February%2010%2C%20failing%20which%20they%20would%20face%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notices%2C%20which%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20seen%2C%20have%20been%20issued%20under%20Haryana%20Recovery%20of%20Damages%20of%20Property%20During%20Disturbance%20of%20Public%20Order%20Act%202021%20and%20under%20section%2069%20of%20Haryana%20Police%20Act%202007%2C%20under%20which%20it%20was%20mandatory%20to%20take%20permission%20before%20giving%20a%20call%20for%20meeting%20or%20gathering%20on%20the%20road%2C%20which%20was%20public%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E13%20Feb%20Farmers%20Delhi%20March%20Update%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E~Farm%20leaders%20met%203%20GOI%20minister%20delegation%3Cbr%3E%5Cn~Another%20meeting%20expected%20before%2013Feb%3Cbr%3E%5Cn~No%20firm%20commitment%20of%20Govt%20on%20MSP%20Guarantee%20Law%3Cbr%3E%5Cn~Farmers%20call%20of%2013%20Feb%20stands%3Cbr%3E%5Cn~Haryana%20police%20is%20raiding%20farm%20leaders%20houses%2C%20notices%20to%20deter%20farmers%20pasted%20!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fqx6bmlyska%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fqx6bmlyska%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20Mann%20(%40ramanmann1974)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Framanmann1974%2Fstatus%2F1755777442051182792%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20BKU%20(SBS)%20spokesperson%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20one%20hand%20the%20Haryana%20police%20was%20targeting%20farmers%20by%20issuing%20them%20notices%20and%20asking%20petrol%20pump%20owners%20not%20to%20give%20them%20petrol%20and%20diesel%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20the%20Central%20government%20ministers%20were%20holding%20meetings%20with%20us.%20This%20shows%20that%20Delhi%20fears%20the%20farmers.%20We%20will%20be%20moving%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%20We%20have%20won%20the%20battle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejveer%20also%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20started%20his%20first%20%E2%80%98Chai%20pe%20Charcha%E2%80%99%20programme%20from%20Yavatmal%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20as%20per%20a%20recent%20report%2C%20the%20number%20of%20farmer%20suicides%20have%20gone%20up%20in%20the%20Marathwada%20region%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20grim%20side%20of%20the%20farm%20crisis%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20do%20not%20want%20to%20create%20trouble%20for%20anybody.%20However%2C%20if%20people%20heading%20to%20IGI%20airport%20or%20those%20going%20to%20weddings%20faced%20trouble%20while%20commuting%20on%20February%2013%2C%20not%20the%20farmers%20but%20the%20Central%20government%20will%20be%20responsible.%20Let%20the%20farmers%20reach%20Delhi%2C%20we%20have%20every%20right%20to%20protest%20and%20inform%20people%20of%20how%20farmers%20were%20being%20ruined%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Gramin%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Samiti%20(GKMS)%20president%20Ranjit%20Singh%20Raju%20from%20Sri%20Ganganagar%20district%2C%20Rajasthan%20also%20said%20that%20farmers%20were%20deliberately%20being%20pushed%20into%20the%20debt%20trap%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20from%20Hanumangarh%2C%20Anoopgarh%20and%20Sri%20Ganganagar%20were%20holding%20tractor%20marches%20for%20the%20February%2013%20Delhi%20Chalo%20protest.%20No%20farmer%20ever%20faces%20scarcity%20of%20wheat%20in%20his%20house.%20A%20farmer%20hardly%20needs%20any%20luxuries%20to%20lead%20his%20life.%20All%20we%20need%20is%20flour%20and%20pickles%20to%20sustain%20and%20rest%20of%20the%20things%20do%20not%20matter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20all%20are%20participating%20in%20the%20protest%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20200%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20have%20planned%20to%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013%2C%20which%20will%20include%20around%20150%20unions%20of%20SKM%20(non-political)%20and%20around%2076%20unions%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20KMSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%20(non-political)%20is%20a%20breakaway%20faction%20of%20the%20SKM%2C%20which%20played%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20forcing%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20take%20back%20three%20farm%20laws%20through%20a%20year-long%20protest%20outside%20Delhi%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%202020%20protest%2C%20several%20unions%20in%20SKM%20went%20in%20different%20directions.%20Some%20fought%20elections%20and%20some%20committed%20to%20remain%20non-political.%20SKM%20(non-%20political)%20has%20been%20born%20of%20this%20churning%20and%20claims%20to%20have%20150%20farm%20unions%20as%20members%20from%20Punjab%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20UP%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKMSC%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20headed%20by%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20claims%20to%20have%20the%20support%20of%2050%20farm%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20other%20SKM%20faction%20under%20Dr%20Darshan%20Pal%2C%20Yadvindra%20Yadav%20and%20others%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20last%20week%2C%20SKM%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20national%20coordination%20committee%20of%20SKM%20held%20an%20online%20meeting%20and%20clarified%20that%20SKM%20has%20not%20given%20any%20call%20for%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99.%20SKM%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20decision%20of%20certain%20kisan%20organisations%20to%20protest%20in%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20SKM%20leaders%20Balbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%2C%20Darshan%20Pal%20and%20Rakesh%20Tikait%20were%20getting%20ready%20for%20the%20February%2016%20%E2%80%98Gramin%20Bharat%20Bandh%E2%80%99%20across%20the%20country%2C%20BKU%20(Ekta%20Ugrahan)%20president%20Joginder%20Singh%20Ugrahan%20was%20already%20leading%20separate%20protests%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Bandh%20call%20was%20given%20by%20the%20SKM%2C%20joint%20platform%20of%20Central%20Trade%20Unions%20and%20Independent%20Sectoral%20Federations%20for%20farmers%2C%20all%20workers%20in%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20including%20ASHA%2C%20Anganwadi%20and%20mid-day%20meal%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20message%2C%20BKU%20Rajewal%20president%20Balbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%20appealed%20to%20people%20to%20join%20the%20Bharat%20Bandh%20on%20February%2016%20and%20raise%20voice%20against%20the%20voiceless%20farmers%2C%20small%20shopkeepers%2C%20and%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20of%20the%20society.%20BKU%20leader%20Rakesh%20Tikait%20also%20appealed%20people%20to%20make%20Bharat%20Bandh%20a%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Kusum%20Arora.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707449904000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09090639%2FGF0FvlvWQAExf0u.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-groups-confront-modi-govt-on-unfulfilled-promises-3-union-ministers-rush-to-meet-them%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unions%20have%20said%20they%20will%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013%20if%20their%20demands%20are%20not%20fulfille