%3A1707444145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107539371%2Cimgsize-23036.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fhow-to-block-and-report-contacts-on-whatsapp-a-step-by-step-guide%2Farticleshow%2F107539393.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you%20feel%20unsafe%2C%20consider%20contacting%20your%20local%20authorities.%20Blocking%20and%20reporting%20contacts%20on%20WhatsApp%20can%20help%20you%20regain%20control%20over%20your%20messaging%20experience%20and%20ensure%20your%20safety%20and%20privacy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fhow-to-block-and-report-contacts-on-whatsapp-a-step-by-step-guide%2Farticleshow%2F107539393.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Our%20Society%20Doesn't%20Want%20the%20Dom%20Community%20to%20Stop%20Their%20Caste-Based%20Work'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08144519%2FRadhika-Iyengar-Book-FB.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EHindu%20rituals%20and%20beliefs%20say%20that%20on%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20only%20someone%20from%20the%20Dom%20community%20can%20provide%20the%20cremation%20fire%20if%20salvation%20is%20to%20be%20achieved.%20The%20Dom%20caste%20comes%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20list%20in%20India.%20Ironically%2C%20those%20whose%20touch%20is%20said%20to%20be%20required%20for%20salvation%20are%20treated%20as%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%20in%20society%3B%20food%20and%20drink%20they%20touch%20is%20avoided%20by%20those%20who%20follow%20the%20oppressive%20caste%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20politically%2C%20before%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20reached%20Varanasi%20to%20file%20his%20nomination%20papers%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20the%20late%20Dom%20raja%20Jagdish%20Chaudhary%20was%20with%20him%20and%20offered%20his%20support%20%E2%80%93%20though%20this%20did%20nothing%20to%20change%20the%20Dom%20community%E2%80%99s%20standard%20of%20living.%20The%20community%20continues%20to%20live%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20society%2C%20with%20basic%20facilities%20out%20of%20their%20reach.%20They%20are%20neither%20recognised%20socially%20nor%20represented%20politically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Varanasi%2C%20called%20the%20city%20of%20life%20and%20death%2C%20Hindu%20last%20rites%20are%20performed%20at%20two%20ghats%2C%20Manikarnika%20and%20Harishchandra.%20The%20Dom%20community%20lives%20near%20the%20Manikarnika%20Ghat.%20Journalist%20Radhika%20Iyengar%20has%20recorded%20their%20daily%20lives%20%E2%80%93%20laced%20as%20it%20is%20with%20death%20%E2%80%93%20in%20her%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EFire%20on%20the%20Ganges%3A%20Life%20among%20the%20Dead%20in%20Banaras%3C%2Fem%3E.%20She%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20her%20research%20and%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EParts%20of%20this%20interview%20were%20conducted%20in%20Hindi%20and%20have%20been%20translated%20into%20English.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20do%20not%20have%20any%20special%20connection%20with%20Varanasi%2C%20you%20grew%20up%20in%20another%20state%2C%20studied%20abroad.%20Then%20why%20Varanasi%3F%20And%20you%20chose%20the%20Dom%20community%20as%20a%20subject%20of%20interest%20%E2%80%93%20what%20was%20the%20reason%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20masters%20in%20journalism%20at%20Columbia%20University%20when%2C%20as%20an%20assignment%2C%20we%20had%20to%20submit%20a%20thesis%20describing%20a%20topic%20we%20would%20like%20to%20report%20on.%20For%20that%2C%20I%20read%20an%20article%20about%20the%20Dom%20community%20and%20I%20became%20interested%20to%20know%20more%20about%20them.%20So%20I%20started%20searching%2C%20but%20whatever%20information%20I%20could%20find%20about%20them%20at%20that%20time%20was%20very%20limited%2C%20only%20about%20their%20work%20at%20the%20crematoriums.%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20more%20about%20other%20aspects%20of%20their%20lives%E2%80%A6%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20work%20at%20a%20cremation%20ground%2C%20how%20they%20felt%2C%20how%20they%20were%20constantly%20close%20to%20the%20fire%2C%20how%20risky%20the%20job%20was.%20What%20effect%20does%20it%20have%20physically%3F%20How%20do%20they%20cope%20with%20these%20everyday%20problems%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20about%20the%20children%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20getting%20a%20good%20education%2C%20whether%20the%20schools%20are%20able%20to%20prepare%20them%20in%20any%20way%2C%20whether%20the%20changing%20environment%20and%20coming%20of%20the%20internet%20etc.%20is%20having%20any%20effect%20on%20them.%20And%20then%20the%20women%20of%20the%20community%20%E2%80%93%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20about%20them.%20What%20is%20their%20life%20like%2C%20what%20are%20their%20dreams%20%E2%80%93%20do%20they%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20go%20out%20of%20the%20house%20and%20earn%20their%20living%3F%20I%20was%20curious%20to%20know%20all%20this%2C%20but%20there%20was%20nothing%20recorded%20about%20it%20anywhere.%20This%20is%20where%20my%20desire%20to%20research%20this%20community%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20book%20started%20taking%20shape.%20It%20took%20me%20eight%20years%20to%20write.%20I%20started%20in%202015%20and%20completed%20it%20in%20early%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlmost%20every%20aspect%20of%20Varanasi%20has%20been%20well%20documented%20%E2%80%93%20the%20ghats%2C%20the%20shops%2C%20the%20stories%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20and%20has%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20attention%20for%20everything%20from%20tourism%20to%20politics.%20But%20there%20has%20not%20been%20enough%20talk%20about%20the%20Dom%20community.%20Are%20the%20writers%20indifferent%20or%20does%20it%20seem%20like%20a%20privileged%20gaze%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcademic%20work%20has%20been%20done%20about%20the%20Dom%20community%20but%20this%20too%20is%20limited%20to%20the%20work%20done%20at%20the%20cremation%20ground%3B%20there%20has%20been%20no%20talk%20about%20their%20lives.%20There%20is%20no%20detail%20about%20the%20community%20%E2%80%93%20the%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20who%20belong%20to%20it.%20I%20feel%20that%20this%20is%20not%20visible%20because%20people%20of%20dominant%20castes%20do%20not%20even%20want%20to%20know%20about%20them.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20much%20to%20them%2C%20as%20long%20as%20there%20is%20a%20Dom%20available%20to%20work%20at%20the%20cremation%20ground%2C%20everything%20is%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20privileged%20lens%20because%20it%20is%20convenient%20for%20people%20like%20us%20to%20remain%20indifferent%20or%20neutral%20towards%20their%20existence%20or%20non-existence.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20they%20have%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20last%20rites%2C%20but%20apart%20from%20that%20no%20one%20cares%20what%20life%20they%20are%20living%2C%20what%20conditions%20they%20are%20living%20in%2C%20what%20difficulties%20they%20are%20facing.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20I%20feel%20that%20people%20of%20dominant%20castes%20live%20in%20their%20own%20world%2C%20everyone%20wants%20to%20remain%20the%20same.%20In%20the%20kind%20of%20society%20we%20live%20in%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20talk%20about%20differences%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98us%20versus%20them%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20is%20about%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20gender%20or%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20also%20like%20to%20add%20that%20the%20work%20that%20has%20been%20done%20in%20academia%20only%20talks%20about%20men%20and%20not%20about%20Dom%20women.%20There%20are%20many%20things%20which%20are%20shocking%20%E2%80%93%20like%20that%20the%20wood%20they%20are%20getting%20for%20cooking%2C%20they%20are%20taking%20burnt%20wood%20from%20the%20crematorium.%20I%20remember%20Bhola%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20characters%20of%20my%20book%2C%20had%20told%20me%20that%20many%20times%20when%20he%20used%20to%20take%20such%20sticks%20home%20from%20the%20crematorium%2C%20there%20would%20be%20pieces%20of%20meat%20stuck%20on%20them.%20Also%20think%20about%20how%20all%20this%20would%20affect%20the%20mood%20of%20a%20child%2C%20if%20you%20are%20growing%20up%20seeing%20death%2C%20burning%20dead%20bodies%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20thing%20worth%20seeing.%20What%20an%20impact%20it%20will%20have!%20And%20Dom%20children%2C%20aged%20five-six%20years%2C%20who%20are%20from%20poor%20families%2C%20are%20forced%20to%20work%20in%20this%20environment.%20I%20have%20mentioned%20in%20my%20book%20how%20these%20small%20children%20pick%20up%20shrouds%20from%20dead%20bodies%20arriving%20at%20the%20ghat%20and%20sell%20them%20for%20very%20little%20money%20to%20shopkeepers%20who%20wash%20them%2C%20press%20them%20and%20resell%20them.%20These%20children%20are%20doing%20the%20same%20thing%20day%20and%20night%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%20it%20is%20affecting%20them%20deeply%20and%20then%20to%20overcome%20this%2C%20they%20start%20using%20alcohol%20and%20drugs%20from%20a%20young%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENowadays%20it%20is%20often%20heard%20that%20discrimination%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20exist%20anymore%2C%20but%20you%20have%20mentioned%20in%20the%20book%20that%20even%20today%2C%20if%20women%20from%20the%20Dom%20community%20are%20touched%20by%20someone%20by%20mistake%2C%20then%20they%20have%20to%20face%20humiliation.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20also%20been%20hearing%20that%20many%20people%20keep%20saying%20that%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20untouchability%20no%20longer%20exist%20in%20the%20country.%20Listening%20to%20them%2C%20I%20wonder%20what%20imaginary%20world%20these%20people%20are%20living%20in.%20Caste%20is%20the%20reality%20of%20our%20society%2C%20even%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20seen%20this%20in%20my%20experience.%20When%20I%20was%20reporting%20in%20Banaras%2C%20I%20had%20to%20travel%20between%20Chand%20Ghat%20and%20Manikarnika%20Ghat%20for%20field%20work.%20Many%20times%20children%20from%20the%20Dom%20community%20would%20also%20come%20along.%20I%20noticed%20that%20they%20were%20always%20avoiding%20a%20particular%20bylane.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%2C%20we%20were%20taking%20long%20route%20and%20kids%20used%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CDidi%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20that%20street.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Later%20one%20day%20it%20came%20to%20light%20that%20there%20was%20a%20temple%20on%20this%20route%2C%20where%20a%20priest%20used%20to%20scold%20the%20Dom%20children%20and%20shoo%20them%20away%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20saw%20them%20around%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20when%20you%20are%20constantly%20belittled%2C%20made%20fun%20of%2C%20called%20untouchable%2C%20shooed%20away%20from%20the%20temple%2C%20what%20effect%20will%20this%20have%20on%20your%20mind%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20when%20I%20went%20to%20Chand%20Ghat%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20I%20met%20an%20elderly%20couple%2C%20who%20responded%20with%20folded%20hands%20and%20bowed%20shoulders%20in%20response%20to%20%E2%80%98Namaste%E2%80%99.%20This%20was%20a%20shocking%20experience%20for%20me.%20Just%20a%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20news%20came%20that%20an%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20man%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2FDec%2F19%2Fmadhya-pradesh-elderly-dalit-man-torturedfor-not-greeting-dominant-caste-menproperly-2642954.html%5C%22%3Ebeaten%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Dalit%20because%20he%20did%20not%20greet%20him%20with%20folded%20hands.%20So%20all%20this%20has%20settled%20in%20their%20mind%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20the%20believe%20discrimination%20is%20bound%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20perhaps%20this%20is%20where%20their%20identity%20crisis%20begins.%20They%20do%20not%20want%20anyone%20to%20know%20their%20identity%3B%20for%20example%2C%20Bhola%20in%20the%20book%20is%20portrayed%20as%20someone%20very%20particular%20about%20not%20revealing%20his%20caste%20and%20identity%2C%20especially%20in%20school%20and%20college%2C%20so%20that%20no%20one%20knows%20where%20he%20comes%20from.%20Why%20is%20it%20so%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20ashamed%20of%20himself.%20He%20takes%20pride%20in%20being%20a%20Dom%2C%20there%20is%20a%20pride%20in%20his%20identity.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20also%20fears%20that%20if%20he%20tells%20anyone%20about%20his%20background%2C%20they%20will%20distance%20themselves%20from%20him%2C%20ridicule%20him%2C%20or%20boycott%20him%20in%20some%20way%2C%20so%20he%20feels%20he%20needs%20to%20protect%20himself.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20he%20hides%20his%20caste%2C%20his%20identity.%20He%20believes%20that%20in%20this%20way%20he%20can%20move%20ahead%20in%20life.%20Otherwise%20people%20will%20not%20allow%20him%20to%20move%20ahead.%20And%20there%20are%20many%20examples%20of%20this%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India.%20If%20we%20talk%20about%20education%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20examples%20in%20the%20last%20five-ten%20years%20only%20%E2%80%93%20Rohith%20Vemula%2C%20Payal%20Tadvi%2C%20many%20like%20them.%20Discrimination%20is%20everywhere%2C%20in%20every%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20can%20we%20say%20that%20Doms%20are%20satisfied%20with%20their%20lives%20or%20they%20have%20no%20expectations%20from%20anyone%2C%20they%20just%20continue%20to%20live%20like%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20living%20like%20this%20because%20they%20have%20no%20other%20option.%20If%20you%20see%20that%20basti%20where%20those%20people%20live%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20very%20difficult.%20As%20I%20have%20said%20in%20the%20book%2C%20when%20the%20children%20who%20started%20studying%20outside%20and%20went%20to%20hostel%20came%20back%20home%20during%20the%20Covid%20lockdown%2C%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20study%20there.%20There%20is%20a%20one-room%20house%2C%20in%20which%20eight-ten%20people%20are%20living%2C%20parents%20are%20sending%20their%20children%20for%20some%20work%20%E2%80%93%20so%20education%20is%20not%20a%20priority%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20people%20there.%20The%20families%20are%20taking%20the%20children%20out%20of%20school%20and%20sending%20them%20to%20Manikarnika%20Ghat%20to%20work%20because%20%3Cem%3Eghar%20me%20chulha%20jalna%20chahiye%3C%2Fem%3E%20(there%20needs%20to%20be%20food%20in%20the%20house).%20The%20priority%20is%20to%20earn%20money%20because%20that%20will%20support%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20want%20to%20move%20ahead%20in%20life%20but%20they%20do%20not%20think%20that%20they%20will%20ever%20be%20able%20to%20do%20so.%20Bhola%20was%20the%20only%20person%20who%20did%20not%20listen%20to%20anyone%2C%20did%20not%20let%20anyone%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20his%20progress.%20But%20not%20everyone%20can%20do%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20in%20a%20way%2C%20this%20vicious%20cycle%20is%20continuing.%20People%20from%20the%20Dom%20community%2C%20especially%20the%20labourers%2C%20are%20forced%20to%20live%20in%20poverty.%20Generations%20change%20but%20there%20is%20no%20change%20in%20their%20lives.%20Why%20do%20you%20think%20that%20is%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20there%20are%20two%20reasons%20for%20this.%20Let%20me%20tell%20you%20an%20incident.%20The%20American%20man%20whom%20I%20have%20mentioned%20in%20the%20book%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20bear%20the%20expenses%20of%20the%20education%20of%20four%20Dom%20children%20including%20Bhola%2C%20told%20me%20that%20when%20he%20was%20talking%20to%20a%20government%20employee%20regarding%20the%20education%20of%20these%20children%2C%20he%20turned%20around%20and%20said%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3ETo%20murda%20kaun%20jalayega%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Who%20will%20burn%20the%20corpses%20then%3F)%20This%20employee%20was%20against%20educating%20these%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20reason%20is%20that%20society%20itself%20does%20not%20want%20Dom%20children%20to%20leave%20this%20work%20and%20go%20out.%20The%20other%20aspect%20is%20that%20people%20within%20the%20community%20also%20think%20the%20same%20way.%20I%20talked%20to%20many%20of%20them%20who%20believe%20that%20only%20they%20can%20provide%20%3Cem%3Emoksha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(salvation)%2C%20that%20Shiva%20has%20given%20this%20boon%20only%20to%20them.%20One%20of%20them%20had%20told%20me%2C%20%3Cem%3EChahe%20raja%20ho%20ya%20fakeer%2C%20ant%20me%20Chaudhary%20sahab%20ka%20pair%20pakadna%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Be%20it%20a%20king%20or%20a%20beggar%2C%20in%20the%20end%20one%20has%20to%20hold%20Chaudhary%20ji%E2%80%99s%20feet).%20So%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20pride%20attached%20to%20the%20work%20they%20do%20and%20this%20is%20because%20they%20want%20to%20justify%20their%20existence%20in%20society.%20That%20society%20which%20otherwise%20keeps%20a%20distance%20from%20them%2C%20considers%20them%20untouchable%20and%20does%20not%20respect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20is%20that%20society%20does%20not%20want%20them%20to%20be%20successful%20in%20life%2C%20which%20we%20saw%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Bhola.%20He%20hid%20his%20identity%20in%20college%20because%20he%20felt%20that%20if%20anyone%2C%20even%20any%20teacher%2C%20came%20to%20know%20about%20this%2C%20they%20would%20put%20some%20kind%20of%20hurdle%20in%20his%20path.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20Dom%20community%20thinks%20that%20they%20are%20fulfilling%20their%20God-given%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20talk%20about%20Dom%20women.%20Varanasi%20is%20transforming%2C%20moving%20on%20the%20path%20of%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20women%20of%20Chand%20Ghat%20are%20left%20far%20behind%2C%20where%20they%20do%20not%20even%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20go%20out%20without%20covering%20their%20heads.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20this%20is%20an%20orthodox%20community%20so%20there%20is%20patriarchy.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20they%20are%20living%20on%20the%20intersection%20of%20caste%2C%20gender%20and%20poverty.%20I%20met%20a%20woman%20while%20she%20was%20cooking%20in%20a%20very%20small%20one-room%20house%20without%20electricity%20during%20the%20scorching%20summer%20season.%20When%20I%20asked%20her%20to%20go%20out%20of%20the%20house%20after%20finishing%20her%20work%2C%20she%20told%20me%20that%20she%20had%20not%20received%20permission%20from%20her%20husband%20to%20do%20so.%20This%20means%20that%20she%20cannot%20even%20step%20out%20of%20the%20house%20on%20her%20own%20will.%20Then%20if%20they%20have%20to%20go%20out%20somewhere%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20cover%20their%20heads.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20this%20but%20they%20have%20to%20do%20it.%20Now%20it%20has%20become%20normal%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20luckily%20now%20change%20is%20coming.%20I%20have%20mentioned%20in%20the%20book%20how%20Bhola%20has%20taken%20three%20of%20his%20nieces%20to%20the%20city%20where%20he%20is%20now%20working.%20This%20is%20a%20big%20thing%20for%20a%20community%20which%20stops%20the%20movement%20of%20its%20daughters%20at%20the%20age%20of%2012-13%20and%20starts%20thinking%20about%20their%20marriage.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20those%20girls%20are%20thinking%20about%20their%20future%20instead%20of%20their%20household%2C%20a%20life%20in%20which%20they%20themselves%20are%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20not%20other%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20some%20time%20now%2C%20caste%20has%20become%20an%20important%20part%20of%20political%20discourse.%20Where%20do%20you%20find%20the%20Dom%20community%20in%20this%3F%20There%20is%20no%20one%20to%20represent%20them%20politically%2C%20to%20ensure%20their%20participation%20in%20society%2C%20to%20talk%20about%20them%20or%20to%20raise%20their%20local%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20new%20things%20are%20happening%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20some%20people%20are%20angry%20about%20it%2C%20some%20are%20happy%2C%20but%20they%20are%20accepting%20the%20changes%20that%20something%20new%20is%20happening.%20When%20late%20Dom%20Raja%20Jagdish%20Choudhary%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri%2C%20his%20son%20Om%20Choudhary%20went%20to%20receive%20the%20award%20on%20his%20behalf%20and%20said%20that%20it%20was%20good%20that%20Doms%20were%20also%20getting%20some%20recognition.%20When%20I%20asked%20a%20Dom%20woman%20about%20this%2C%20she%20said%20that%20all%20this%20is%20very%20good%2C%20but%20the%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99%20they%20are%20talking%20about%20has%20not%20reached%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20talk%20about%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebastis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(settlements)%20that%20I%20have%20visited.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20problems%20in%20the%20settlement%2C%20which%20are%20common%20in%20such%20areas%2C%20water%20shortage%2C%20not%20enough%20space%20to%20live%2C%20no%20toilets%2C%20etc.%20There%20are%20certainly%20government%20schemes%20but%20people%20are%20not%20aware%20about%20them.%20Even%20if%20they%20know%2C%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20necessary%20records%20or%20complete%20documents.%20I%20asked%20them%20if%20they%20had%20any%20activists%20or%20anyone%20who%20would%20fight%20for%20their%20cause%20whenever%20they%20raised%20it%2C%20the%20answer%20I%20got%20was%20that%20people%20are%20so%20engrossed%20in%20their%20own%20lives%20that%20they%20have%20no%20time%20to%20rally%20around%20anything%20else.%20There%20is%20no%20time%20to%20fight.%20They%20are%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20they%20have%20to%20dig%20a%20well%20every%20day%20if%20they%20want%20to%20drink%20water%2C%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eso%20their%20worry%20is%20always%20whether%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20get%20their%20next%20meal.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20difficult%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20the%20Dom%20Raja%20concept%20provide%20any%20benefit%20to%20the%20people%20as%20a%20community%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20like%20that.%20The%20same%20woman%20told%20me%20that%20you%20are%20honouring%20Dom%20Raja%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20that%20is%20great%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20helping%20the%20Doms%20as%20a%20community%2C%20who%20are%20living%20at%20the%20lowest%20rung%20of%20society.%20They%20hope%20that%20there%20can%20be%20a%20change%20after%20the%20general%20elections%20of%202024%2C%20but%20there%20are%20also%20reports%20that%20their%20settlement%20can%20be%20demolished%2C%20so%20there%20is%20also%20a%20kind%20of%20fear%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20women%20generally%20do%20not%20go%20to%20the%20cremation%20ground.%20You%20reported%20for%20such%20a%20long%20time%2C%20did%20your%20gender%20become%20any%20hindrance%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20absolutely.%20Whoever%20has%20been%20to%20Manikarnika%20Ghat%20knows%20that%20there%20are%20mostly%20men%20there%2C%20wood%20sellers%2C%20samagri%20sellers%2C%20%3Cem%3EShav%20Yatris%3C%2Fem%3E%20(funeral%20processions)%2C%20relatives%20of%20the%20deceased%20are%20all%20men%2C%20so%20in%20such%20a%20situation%20a%20woman%20holding%20a%20dictaphone%20in%20one%20hand%2C%20a%20notebook%20in%20the%20other%20and%20a%20camera%20around%20her%20neck%20will%20naturally%20get%20attention.%20In%20the%20beginning%20I%20used%20to%20feel%20that%20all%20the%20eyes%20were%20constantly%20on%20me.%20It%20took%20me%20a%20long%20time%20to%20become%20normal%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20tried%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20Dom%20men%20working%20at%20the%20ghat%2C%20they%20too%20were%20not%20comfortable.%20The%20first%20thing%20was%20that%20I%20was%20an%20outsider%20who%20was%20asking%20questions%20about%20their%20life.%20Second%2C%20I%20am%20a%20woman.%20They%20are%20not%20used%20to%20talking%20to%20women.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work%20to%20overcome%20this.%20But%20when%20I%20kept%20going%20again%20and%20again%2C%20they%20started%20trusting%20me.%20(Laughs)%20But%20still%20there%20was%20one%20person%20who%20always%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20some%20undercover%20cop%20and%20used%20to%20run%20away%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20saw%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20come%20from%20a%20world%20very%20different%20from%20the%20challenges%20of%20this%20community%2C%20so%20while%20writing%20the%20book%2C%20how%20much%20did%20pay%20attention%20to%20not%20being%20judgmental%20about%20their%20situation%2C%20their%20lives%2C%20society%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20have%20also%20written%20in%20the%20book%2C%20I%20was%20very%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20come%20from%20a%20privileged%20class%20and%20caste%20and%20I%20have%20taken%20special%20care%20of%20this%20in%20my%20reporting%20and%20writing.%20I%20also%20talked%20to%20my%20editor%20about%20this.%20We%20are%20taught%20in%20journalism%20that%20while%20telling%20someone%E2%80%99s%20story%2C%20we%20should%20not%20add%20our%20own%20opinion%20and%20I%20kept%20this%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20written%20from%20my%20perspective%2C%20but%20only%20where%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20add%20my%20experience.%20My%20aim%20was%20to%20record%20their%20lives%2C%20I%20listened%20to%20them%20carefully.%20But%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20intensive%20research%20is%20done%2C%20it%20cannot%20replace%20the%20lived%20experience%2C%20so%20I%20was%20recording%20only%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAt%20some%20points%2C%20your%20book%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%202015%20film%20%3Cem%3EMasaan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20book%2C%20you%20have%20thanked%20the%20actor%20who%20played%20the%20protaganist%20in%20the%20film.%20Is%20there%20any%20connection%20between%20the%20book%20and%20the%20film%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20very%20interesting%20thing%20that%20whoever%20has%20any%20memory%20related%20to%20the%20Dom%20community%20in%20their%20minds%2C%20it%20is%20from%20this%20film.%20But%20this%20is%20a%20very%20important%20film.%20During%20my%20reporting%2C%20I%20brought%20some%20children%20of%20Chand%20Ghat%20(who%20are%20mentioned%20in%20the%20book)%20to%20my%20guest%20house%20and%20showed%20them%20this%20film.%20I%20wanted%20them%20to%20watch%20it.%20Till%20that%20time%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20that%20a%20film%20was%20made%20on%20their%20community%2C%20so%20they%20were%20very%20excited.%20But%20when%20they%20saw%20it%2C%20they%20said%20that%20the%20film%20is%20good%2C%20but%20our%20life%20is%20very%20different%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20young%20at%20that%20time%2C%20but%20if%20you%20read%20the%20book%2C%20you%20will%20get%20to%20know%20that%20in%20present%2C%20the%20lives%20of%20two%20of%20them%20have%20followed%20almost%20the%20same%20trajectory%20as%20that%20of%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20character%20Deepak.%20As%20part%20of%20my%20research%2C%20I%20interviewed%20actor%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20to%20find%20out%20what%20his%20experience%20was%20of%20working%20at%20the%20crematorium.%20But%20all%20this%20was%20a%20small%20part%20of%20the%20research%2C%20apart%20from%20this%20I%20had%20looked%20at%20various%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20this%20interview%20in%20Hindi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F267240%2Fvaranasi-dom-community-radhika-iyengar-interview%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707442202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08144519%2FRadhika-Iyengar-Book-FB.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Four-society-doesnt-want-the-dom-community-to-stop-their-caste-based-work%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20conversation%20with%20Radhika%20Iyengar%2C%20the%20author%20of%20'Fire%20on%20the%20Ganges'%2C%20about%20her%20research%20into%20the%20Dom%20community%20and%20their%20daily%20lives%20and%20ambitions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Four-society-doesnt-want-the-dom-community-to-stop-their-caste-based-work%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Military%20Personnel%20in%20Maldives%20Will%20Be%20Replaced%20With%20'Competent%20Indian%20Technical%20Personnel'%3A%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03232814%2FMuizzu-and-Modi.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20India%20has%20announced%20that%20military%20personnel%20currently%20operating%20aviation%20platforms%20in%20the%20Maldives%20will%20be%20substituted%20with%20%E2%80%9Ccompetent%20Indian%20technical%20personnel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20last%20week%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20of%20the%20core%20group%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20foreign%20ministry%20stated%20that%20India%20had%20agreed%20to%20%E2%80%9Creplace%E2%80%9D%20the%20military%20personnel%20in%20one%20of%20the%20three%20aircraft%20by%20March%2010%20and%20would%20complete%20%E2%80%9Creplacing%E2%80%9D%20the%20personnel%20in%20the%20other%20two%20by%20May%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37511%2FFirst_meeting_of_the_IndiaMaldives_High_Level_Core_Group%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20external%20affair%E2%80%99s%20readout%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20give%20the%20details%20and%20merely%20said%20that%20both%20countries%20had%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%20on%20a%20set%20of%20mutually%20workable%20solutions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Findian-coast-guard-boats-maldives-muizzu-opposition-parliament%5C%22%3EOn%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Maldivian%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20declared%20that%20India%20had%20agreed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwithdraw%E2%80%9D%20its%20military%20personnel.%20That%20marked%20the%20first%20instance%20where%20the%20Maldives%20explicitly%20said%20that%20Indian%20personnel%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cwithdrawn%2C%E2%80%9D%20departing%20from%20the%20previous%20use%20of%20the%20ambiguous%20term%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-to-replace-military-personnel-operating-aircraft-helicopters-maldives%5C%22%3Ereplace%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20India%20finally%20acknowledged%20that%20military%20personnel%20will%20be%20withdrawn%2C%20albeit%20without%20explicitly%20using%20that%20term.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20say%20that%20the%20present%20personnel%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20competent%20Indian%20technical%20personnel%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20at%20the%20weekly%20briefing%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expertise%20for%20operating%20these%20platforms%20are%20usually%20found%20among%20ex-servicemen%20who%20had%20operated%20such%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20withdrawal%20in%20his%20inaugural%20speech%20at%20the%20opening%20of%20parliament%2C%20Muizzu%20noted%20that%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20had%20been%20one%20of%20the%20key%20reasons%20for%20his%20successful%20electoral%20victory%20in%20the%20presidential%20elections.%20This%20demand%20had%20been%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99%20campaign%2C%20which%20began%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20officially%20requested%20India%20to%20withdraw%20its%20troops.%20Approximately%2080%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20are%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives%20to%20operate%20two%20helicopters%20and%20a%20Dornier%20plane%20for%20medical%20evacuation%20and%20search%20and%20rescue%20missions.%20During%20his%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Dubai%2C%20both%20leaders%20agreed%20to%20establish%20a%20committee%20of%20officials%20to%20address%20this%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20group%E2%80%99s%20inaugural%20meeting%20last%20month%2C%20Muizzu%20set%20a%20March%2015%20ultimatum%2C%20signalling%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20desire%20for%20prompt%20action%20from%20India%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707413848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03232814%2FMuizzu-and-Modi.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmilitary-personnel-in-maldives-will-be-replaced-with-competent-indian-technical-personnel-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20February%205%20(Monday)%2C%20Maldivian%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20declared%20that%20India%20had%20agreed%20to%20%26quot%3Bwithdraw%26quot%3B%20its%20military%20personnel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmilitary-personnel-in-maldives-will-be-replaced-with-competent-indian-technical-personnel-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20Educating%20Rita%3A%20The%20Early%20Years%20of%20Brinda%20Karat's%20Political%20Career%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08223752%2FKT-8-FEB-B-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20discuss%20her%20memoir%20%3Cem%3EAn%20Education%20for%20Rita%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Brinda%20Karat%20reveals%20that%20Rita%20was%20the%20name%20she%20was%20first%20given%20when%20she%20joined%20the%20CPI(M).%20One%20of%20her%20colleagues%20called%20Chandrabhan%2C%20a%20textile%20worker%20and%20former%20wrestler%2C%20could%20never%20pronounce%20her%20name%20Brinda.%20He%20called%20her%20Birinder%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CMy%20repeated%20efforts%20to%20correct%20his%20pronunciation%20had%20come%20to%20nought.%20It%20was%20probably%20with%20relief%20that%20he%20enthusiastically%20welcomed%20the%20suggestion%20to%20rename%20me.%20He%20said%3A%20%E2%80%98Let%E2%80%99s%20have%20a%20name%20that%20is%20easy%20to%20pronounce.%20We%20will%20call%20you%20Rita%E2%80%99.%20From%20that%20day%20for%20the%20next%20ten%20years%2C%20I%20was%20known%20as%20Comrade%20Rita.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2035-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Karat%20reveals%20that%20her%20first%20big%20corporate%20battle%20happened%20when%20she%20was%20working%20for%20Air%20India%20in%20London%20in%201967.%20It%20had%20to%20do%20with%20the%20right%20to%20wear%20sarees%20rather%20than%20a%20mini%20skirt.%20She%20was%2020%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20London%2C%20where%20she%20immersed%20herself%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20liberation%20struggle%20of%20Vietnam%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20part%20of%20the%20famous%20Grosvenor%20Square%20protests%20of%201968%2C%20that%20she%20was%20first%20drawn%20to%20Marxism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20return%20to%20India%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Communist%20Party%20Marxist%20and%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Prakash%20Karat.%20When%20they%20decided%20to%20get%20married%2C%20they%20chose%20November%207%2C%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Russian%20Revolution.%20But%2C%20actually%2C%20in%201917%2C%20the%20date%20in%20Russia%20was%2012%20days%20earlier%20(October%2025).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20reveals%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20being%20an%20ideal%20wife%20%E2%80%93%20communist%20or%20otherwise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20challenges%20she%20faced%20was%20to%20navigate%20a%20career%20for%20herself%20around%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20position%20as%20a%20senior%20member%20of%20the%20same%20party%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20CPM%20from%202005%20to%202015.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20often%20my%20own%20identity%20as%20a%20communist%2C%20as%20a%20woman%2C%20as%20a%20whole-timer%20of%20the%20party%20for%20so%20many%20decades%2C%20was%20all%20conflated%20with%20my%20being%20Prakash%E2%80%99s%20wife.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20book%20is%20about%20the%20period%20from%201975%20to%201985%2C%20a%20decade%20during%20which%20she%20spent%20time%20in%20jail%20where%20she%20met%20Charles%20Sobhraj%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20contempt%20of%20court%20and%20found%20guilty%20and%20punished.%20He%20was%20involved%20in%20several%20anti-dowry%20campaigns%20and%20worked%20diligently%20to%20help%20the%20Sikh%20community%20during%20the%20dreadful%20killings%20of%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Janata%20government%20years%2C%20when%20she%20was%20working%20with%20textile%20mill%20workers%2C%20Karat%20was%20falsely%20accused%20of%20trying%20to%20murder%20a%20police%20inspector%20whereas%20the%20truth%20was%20that%20he%20was%20guilty%20of%20beating%20her.%20She%20ended%20up%20spending%20time%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgG9ZWwzzbDg%3Fsi%3D5re9gjk5IgAW89Fk%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707412230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08223752%2FKT-8-FEB-B-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-educating-rita-the-early-years-of-brinda-karats-political-career%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20to%20discuss%20her%20memoir%20'An%20Education%20for%20Rita'%2C%20Brinda%20Karat%20tells%20Karan%20Thapar%20that%20Rita%20was%20the%20name%20she%20was%20first%20given%20when%20she%20joined%20the%20CPI(M).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-educating-rita-the-early-years-of-brinda-karats-political-career%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Rejects%20Allegations%20of%20Election%20Interference%2C%20Points%20Finger%20at%20Ottawa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21173817%2F1024px-The_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_with_the_Prime_Minister_of_Canada_Mr._Justin_Trudeau_at_Hyderabad_House_in_New_Delhi_on_February_23_2018_1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20public%20inquiry%20into%20foreign%20interference%20in%20elections%20formally%20began%20to%20examine%20India%E2%80%99s%20role%2C%20New%20Delhi%20rebuffed%20the%20allegations%20and%20contended%20that%20it%20was%20Ottawa%20that%20interfered%20in%20the%20internal%20affairs%20of%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanadas-probe-panel-to-examine-indias-alleged-role-in-the-last-two-federal-elections%5C%22%3EOver%20two%20weeks%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20Public%20Inquiry%20into%20Foreign%20Interference%20in%20Federal%20Electoral%20Processes%20and%20Democratic%20Institutions%20announced%20that%20it%20has%20requested%20the%20Canadian%20government%20to%20provide%20information%20%E2%80%9Crelating%20to%20alleged%20interference%20by%20India%20related%20to%20the%202019%20and%202021%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20its%20launch%20in%20September%202023%2C%20the%20Commission%20explicitly%20stated%20its%20intention%20to%20investigate%20interference%20by%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20unspecified%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20actors%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20inquiries.%20In%20the%20recent%20press%20release%2C%20expanded%20its%20investigation%20to%20include%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20expressed%20outrage%20over%20the%20inclusion%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20media%20reports%20about%20the%20Canadian%20Commission%20enquiring%20into%20foreign%20interference.%20We%20strongly%20reject%20such%20baseless%20allegations%20of%20Indian%20interference%20in%20Canadian%20elections.%20It%20is%20not%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20policy%20to%20interfere%20in%20democratic%20processes%20of%20other%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20at%20the%20weekly%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20he%20countered%20by%20accusing%20Ottawa%20of%20meddling%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20politics.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20Canada%20which%20has%20been%20interfering%20in%20our%20internal%20affairs.%20We%20have%20been%20raising%20this%20issue%20regularly%20with%20them.%20We%20continue%20to%20call%20on%20Canada%20to%20take%20effective%20measures%20to%20address%20our%20core%20concerns%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Canadian%20outlet%20had%20last%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobalnews.ca%2Fnews%2F10264872%2Fcanada-china-foreign-interference-elections-csis-report%2F%5C%22%3Epublished%20a%20declassified%20intelligence%20briefing%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20February%202023%20which%20said%20that%20China%20and%20India%20had%20both%20interfered%20in%20last%20two%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202023%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20alleged%20India%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20shooting%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Harpreet%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20had%20been%20designated%20as%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20by%20Indian%20security%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20vehemently%20refuted%20the%20accusation%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20expulsion%20of%20one%20diplomat%20from%20each%20nation.%20Additionally%2C%20India%20suspended%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%2C%20which%20were%20later%20resumed%20after%20approximately%20one%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20diplomatic%20parity%2C%20Ottawa%20had%20to%20recall%20over%2040%20diplomats.%20India%20had%20then%20claimed%20that%20Canadian%20diplomats%20were%20interfering%20in%20Indian%20politics%20but%20had%20not%20shared%20any%20public%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Indian%20officials%20had%20repeatedly%20pointed%20to%20statements%20made%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Trudeau%20during%20the%20farmers%20protest%20in%20India%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ftrudeau-canada-farmer-protest-internal-affair%5C%22%3Ecompelling%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Canadian%20interference.%20Moreover%2C%20India%20has%20expressed%20frustration%20with%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20perceived%20lack%20of%20action%20in%20curbing%20the%20activities%20of%20pro-Khalistani%20groups%20within%20its%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20Commission%20is%20scheduled%20to%20issue%20an%20interim%20report%20by%20May%203%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20delivery%20of%20its%20final%20report%20by%20the%20year%E2%80%99s%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707411632000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21173817%2F1024px-The_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_with_the_Prime_Minister_of_Canada_Mr._Justin_Trudeau_at_Hyderabad_House_in_New_Delhi_on_February_23_2018_1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-rejects-allegations-of-election-interference-points-finger-at-ottawa%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada%20initiated%20a%20formal%20enquiry%20of%20India's%20alleged%20role%20in%20interfering%20with%20the%20country's%20elections.%20In%20response%2C%20New%20Delhi%20vehemently%20refuted%20the%20accusations%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20actually%20Ottawa%20that%20had%20interfered%20in%20India's%20internal%20affairs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-rejects-allegations-of-election-interference-points-finger-at-ottawa%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2