%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKambli%2C%20a%20car%20dealer%20from%20Pune%2C%20was%20first%20spotted%20by%20hotel%20staff%20lying%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20his%20room%2C%20bleeding%20profusely%20from%20his%20nose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnjali%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20a%20restaurant%20at%20the%20Kolkata%20airport%2C%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Kambli%2C%20who%20she%20had%20befriended%20at%20the%20airport%20last%20year%2C%20said%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20led%20to%20complications%20since%20Anjali%20was%20already%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Rakesh%2C%20who%20had%20been%20pressurising%20her%20to%20marry%20him.%20What%20complicated%20the%20issue%20further%20was%20that%20the%20victim%20had%20intimate%20pictures%20with%20her%20on%20his%20phone%2C%20Anjali%20said%20during%20her%20interrogation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prompted%20the%20couple%20-%20Anjali%20and%20Rakesh%20-%20to%20devise%20a%20plan%20to%20confront%20Kambli%20over%20those%20photos.%20They%20had%20earlier%20planned%20to%20meet%20at%20the%20Kolkata%20airport%2C%20but%20Kambli%20moved%20it%20to%20Guwahati%2C%20where%20he%20booked%20a%20room%20in%20the%20five-star%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20flew%20to%20Guwahati%20together%20but%20parted%20their%20ways%20on%20reaching%20Guwahati.%20Rakesh%20had%20even%20booked%20a%20room%20for%20himself%20in%20the%20same%20hotel%20without%20Kambli's%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20plan%2C%20Anjali%20was%20joined%20by%20Kambli%20in%20the%20city%20and%20they%20checked%20in%20at%20the%20hotel%20together%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Rakesh%20arrived%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20meeting%2C%20Rakesh's%20arrival%20enraged%20Kambli%20and%20a%20fight%20erupted%20between%20the%20two.%20The%20fight%20left%20Kambli%20injured%2C%20seeing%20which%20the%20couple%20fled.%20They%20also%20took%20away%20two%20mobile%20phones%20belonging%20to%20Kambli%20-%20which%20allegedly%20had%20their%20intimate%20ph