2Register%20Live-In%20Relationships%20Or%20Face%206-Month%20Jail%3A%20Uttarakhand%20Civil%20Code%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndividuals%20in%2C%20or%20planning%20to%20enter%2C%20live-in%20relationships%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Futtarakhand%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUttarakhand%3C%2Fa%3E%20must%20register%20themselves%20with%20district%20officials%20once%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Funiform-civil-code%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniform%20Civil%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20becomes%20law%2C%20with%20parental%20consent%20required%20for%20those%20below%20the%20age%20of%2021%20who%20wish%20to%20live%20together.%20Mandatory%20registration%20of%20such%20relationships%20extends%20to%20individuals%20who%20%26quot%3Bany%20resident%20of%20Uttarakhand...%20in%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20outside%20the%20State%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Flive-in-relationships%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELive-in%20relationships%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20not%20be%20registered%20in%20cases%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bagainst%20public%20policy%20and%20morality%26quot%3B%2C%20if%20one%20partner%20is%20married%20or%20in%20another%20relationship%2C%20if%20one%20partner%20is%20a%20minor%2C%20and%20if%20consent%20of%20one%20partner%20was%20obtained%20by%20%26quot%3Bcoercion%2C%20fraud%2C%20or%20misrepresentation%20(with%20regard%20to%20identity)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20told%20NDTV%20a%20website%20is%20being%20prepped%20to%20accept%20details%20of%20live-in%20relationship%2C%20which%20will%20be%20verified%20with%20the%20District%20Registrar%2C%20who%20will%20conduct%20a%20%26quot%3Bsummary%20inquiry%26quot%3B%20to%20establish%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20relationship.%20To%20do%20so%2C%20he%20may%20summon%20either%20or%20both%20partners%2C%20or%20anybody%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20registration%20be%20refused%2C%20the%20Registrar%20must%20inform%20in%20writing%20his%2Fher%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Btermination%26quot%3B%20of%20registered%20live-in%20relationships%20requires%20a%20written%20statement%2C%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bprescribed%20format%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20invite%20police%20investigation%20if%20the%20Registrar%20feels%20reasons%20for%20the%20relationship%20ending%20are%20%26quot%3Bincorrect%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%26quot%3B.%20Parents%20or%20guardians%20of%20those%20under%2021%20will%20also%20be%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFailure%20to%20submit%20live-in%20relationship%20declarations%2C%20or%20providing%20false%20information%2C%20could%20land%20one%20in%20jail%20for%20three%20months%2C%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%20Anyone%20who%20fails%20to%20register%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20will%20face%20a%20maximum%20of%20six%20months%20in%20jail%2C%20be%20fined%20Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%20Even%20a%20delay%20in%20registration%2C%20by%20as%20little%20as%20a%20month%2C%20will%20trigger%20a%20jail%20term%20of%20up%20to%20three%20months%2C%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20key%20points%20in%20the%20section%20on%20live-in%20relationships%20in%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20that%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Assembly%20Tuesday%20morning%20are%20that%20children%20born%20out%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20will%20receive%20legal%20recognition%3B%20i.e.%2C%20they%20%26quot%3Bshall%20be%20a%20legitimate%20child%20of%20the%20couple%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-is-uttarakhands-uniform-civil-code-bill-5002455%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUttarakhand%20Takes%20Up%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%3A%20Bill%20Explained%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20the%20same%20official%20told%20NDTV%2C%20means%20%26quot%3Brights%20of%20all%20children%20born%20out%20of%20wedlock%2C%20in%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20or%20via%20incubation%2C%20will%20be%20the%20same...%20no%20child%20can%20be%20defined%20as%20'illegitimate'%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20%26quot%3Ball%20children%20will%20have%20equal%20rights%20in%20inheritance%20(including%20parental%20property)%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20drawing%20attention%20to%20the%20language%20of%20the%20UCC%2C%20which%20refers%20to%20%26quot%3Bchild%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20%26quot%3Bson%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bdaughter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20%26quot%3Bdeserted%20by%20her%20live-in%20partner%26quot%3B%20can%20claim%20maintenance%2C%20the%20UCC%20draft%20also%20said%2C%20although%20it%20does%20not%20specify%20what%20constitutes%20%26quot%3Bdesertion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUttarakhand's%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%3A%20Explained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20or%20UCC%20refers%20to%20a%20set%20of%20laws%20applicable%20to%20all%20citizens%2C%20and%20is%20not%20based%20on%20religion%20when%20dealing%20with%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20inheritance%2C%20and%20adoption%2C%20among%20other%20personal%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20common%20civil%20code%20for%20Uttarakhand%20was%20one%20of%20the%20major%20poll%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20last%20year's%20assembly%20election%2C%20which%20the%20party%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20State-appointed%20panel%2C%20led%20by%20a%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20has%20drafted%20a%20749-page%20document%20based%20on%20a%20reported%202.33%20lakh%20pieces%20of%20written%20feedback%20and%20engagement%20with%2060%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20proposals%20include%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20polygamy%20and%20child%20marriage%2C%20a%20standardised%20marriageable%20age%20for%20girls%20across%20all%20faiths%2C%20and%20a%20uniform%20process%20for%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand's%20UCC%20also%20seeks%20to%20ban%20practices%20like%20'%3Cem%3Ehalala%3C%2Fem%3E'%20and%20'%3Cem%3Eiddat%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20which%20are%20the%20Islamic%20practices%20a%20woman%20must%20go%20through%20after%20a%20divorce%20or%20the%20death%20of%20the%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-to-implement-uniform-civil-code-in-2024-tribals-to-be-exempted-chief-minister-himanta-biswa-sarma-4842909%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssam%20To%20Implement%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20In%202024%2C%20Tribals%20Exempt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand%20isn't%20the%20only%20state%20to%20be%20pushing%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%2C%20with%20Assam%2C%20another%20BJP-ruled%20state%20announcing%20plans%20to%20implement%20similar%20rules%20later%20this%20year.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20though%2C%20tribal%20communities%20-%20a%20key%20vote%20bank%20in%20each%20state%20-%20will%20be%20exempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707204060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkc79p8d8_couple-generic-couple-disagreement-generic-couple-fight-istock_625x300_16_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-uniform-civil-code-live-in-relationships-registration-register-live-in-relationships-or-face-6-month-jail-uttarakhand-civil-code-5003753%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Individuals%20in%2C%20or%20planning%20to%20enter%2C%20live-in%20relationships%20in%20Uttarakhand%20must%20register%20themselves%20with%20district%20officials%20once%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20becomes%20law%2C%20with%20parental%20consent%20required%20for%20those%20below%2021%20who%20wish%20to%20live%20together.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-uniform-civil-code-live-in-relationships-registration-register-live-in-relationships-or-face-6-month-jail-uttarakhand-civil-code-5003753%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-uniform-civil-code-live-in-relationships-registration-register-live-in-relationships-or-face-6-month-jail-uttarakhand-civil-code-5003753%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-uniform-civil-code-live-in-relationships-registration-register-live-in-relationships-or-face-6-month-jail-uttarakhand-civil-code-5003753%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20Revolutionised%20Digital%20Payments%20When%20Cash%20Was%20King%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20faces%20of%20India's%20fintech%20industry%2C%20is%20facing%20a%20big%20crisis%20in%20a%20race%20to%20save%20his%20revolutionary%20digital%20payments%20firm%20-%20Paytm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20faces%20the%20challenge%20to%20keep%20the%20company%20operations%20running%20and%20regain%20investors'%20confidence%20after%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20ordered%20Paytm's%20banking%20arm%20to%20stop%20most%20of%20its%20operations%20from%20March%201%20over%20the%20violation%20of%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20a%20stunning%20twist%20in%20the%20Paytm%20story%2C%20which%20started%20from%20Aligarh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma's%20hometown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20trained%20engineer%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20set%20up%20internet%20connections%20at%20homes%20to%20make%20a%20living%20after%20completing%20his%20education.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20came%20to%20be%20counted%20in%20the%20country's%20top-100%20richest%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20Push%20In%202016%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20was%20founded%20in%202010%20by%20Mr%20Sharma%20as%20a%20pre-paid%20mobile%20bill%20payment%20platform.%20The%20company%20expanded%20to%20facilitating%20online%20instant%20payments%20through%20the%20Unified%20Payments%20Interface%20(UPI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20push%20came%20with%20demonetisation%20in%202016%2C%20when%20Rs%20500%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20currency%20notes%20were%20outlawed%20overnight%2C%20leaving%20millions%20struggling%20for%20cash.%20Many%20moved%20to%20online%20transactions%2C%20and%20Paytm%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20player%2C%20quickly%20becoming%20the%20country's%20premier%20digital%20payments%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIPO%20Backlash%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm's%202021%20IPO%20valuation%20faced%20a%20backlash%20from%20investors%20and%20analysts%20when%20the%20stock%20plummeted%20on%20its%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20IPO%20opened%20on%20November%208%2C%202021%2C%20in%20the%20price%20band%20of%20Rs%202%2C080-2%2C150%20per%20share.%20The%20Paytm%20IPO%20made%20history%20with%20over%20Rs%2018%2C300%20crore%20share%20sale%20making%20it%20the%20largest%20public%20issue%20in%20India's%20corporate%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20company's%20stock%20made%20a%20weak%20debut%20in%20the%20market%20on%20November%2018%20and%20hit%20a%20lower%20circuit%20after%20recording%20about%2020%20per%20cent%20decline%20during%20trading%20hours.%20It%20finally%20closed%20at%20Rs%201%2C560%2C%20down%20by%20about%2027%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20big%20backer%20SoftBank%20recently%20pared%20its%20stake%2C%20while%20other%20key%20investors%20Alibaba%20and%20Buffett's%20Berkshire%20Hathway%20sold%20their%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevenue%20Sources%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20has%20two%20major%20sources%20of%20revenue%20-%20its%20merchant%20payment%20business%20and%20loan%20business.%20Merchant%20payments%20constitutes%20roughly%2060%25%20of%20total%20income%20and%20loans%20account%20for%20about%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fintech%20company%20charges%20merchants%20a%20platform%20fee%20to%20use%20Paytm's%20payment%20gateway%2C%20among%20other%20subscription-based%20services%20and%20products%20such%20as%20a%20soundbox%20and%20card%20swipe%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20provides%20loans%20under%20partnerships%20with%20some%20banks%20and%20non-bank%20financial%20companies%2C%20taking%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20interest.%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20was%20one%20of%20these%20entities%20through%20which%20it%20provided%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERBI%20Crackdown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20last%20week%20ordered%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20to%20wind%20down%20most%20of%20its%20businesses%2C%20including%20deposits%2C%20credit%20products%20and%20its%20popular%20wallet%20by%20February%2029%20for%20%26quot%3Bpersistent%20non-compliances%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsupervisory%20concerns%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20accounts%20created%20on%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20without%20proper%20identification%20were%20one%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20the%20RBI%20imposing%20stringent%20curbs%20on%20the%20company%2C%20reports%20quoted%20sources%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20is%20concerned%20that%20some%20of%20the%20accounts%20could%20have%20been%20used%20for%20money%20laundering%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20assuring%20users%2C%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20has%20described%20the%20RBI's%20action%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bspeed%20bump%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707204000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-11%2Fcac3fqc8_vijay-shekhar-sharma-paytm-reuters-650_625x300_18_November_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-vijay-shekha