ment%22%3A135%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Kiran%20Rao-Aamir%20Khan%20vs%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%20-%20It's%20Complicated%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAamir%20Khan%2C%20ex-wife%20Kiran%20Rao%20and%20Animal%20director%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%20are%20currently%20involved%20in%20a%20three-way%20exchange%20of%20critical%20commentary%2C%20both%20implied%20and%20direct.%20In%20this%2C%20Aamir%20is%20a%20silent%20participant%20but%20also%20the%20fulcrum%20around%20which%20the%20controversy%20has%20coalesced.%20There's%20a%20lot%20to%20unpack%20in%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20which%20began%20with%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%20taking%20aim%20at%20Kiran%20Rao%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%20For%20context%2C%20Mr%20Vanga's%20last%20two%20films%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EAnimal%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EKabir%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20were%20both%20not%20just%20massive%20hits%20but%20also%20widely%20condemned%20for%20their%20glorification%20of%20misogyny%20and%20toxic%20masculinity.%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%20has%20spent%20much%20of%20his%20public%20time%20since%20the%20release%20of%20%3Cem%3EAnimal%3C%2Fem%3E%20defending%20his%20filmmaking%20from%20critics%20who%20warn%20against%20the%20dangers%20of%20portraying%20violence%20against%20and%20debasement%20of%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20break-down%20of%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga's%20charge%20against%20Kiran%20Rao%2C%20her%20rejoinder%2C%20and%20Aamir%20Khan's%20incidental%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESANDEEP%20REDDY%20VANGA%20NAME-CHECKS%20KIRAN%20RAO%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSmFi6RklPBY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDainik%20Bhaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EAnimal%3C%2Fem%3E%20director%20targeted%20Kiran%20Rao%20apropos%20of%20an%20old%20comment%20in%20which%20she%20called%20out%20certain%20