0are%20depicted%20in%20Bollywood%20and%20that%20she%20had%20not%20seen%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga's%20films.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20commented%20on%20Mr%20Sandeep's%20films%20because%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20them.%20I%20have%20often%20spoken%20on%20misogyny%20and%20the%20representation%20of%20women%20on%20screen.%20I%20have%20talked%20about%20it%20on%20various%20platforms%20at%20various%20times.%20But%20I%20have%20never%20taken%20the%20name%20of%20any%20film%20because%20it%20is%20not%20about%20the%20specific%20film.%20Why%20Mr%20Vanga%20has%20assumed%20that%20I%20was%20talking%20about%20his%20film%20you'll%20have%20to%20ask%20him.%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20his%20film%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIS%20THIS%20THE%20LAST%20WORD%2C%20FOR%20ITS%20WORTH%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20X%2C%20the%20official%20handle%20of%20%3Cem%3EAnimal%3C%2Fem%3E%20posted%20indignantly%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20neither%20our%20director%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%20are%20making%20any%20assumptions%20Ms%20Kiran%20Rao.%20It%20is%20a%20fact%20reported%20by%20a%20very%20big%20media%20channel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20neither%20our%20Director%20Mr%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fimvangasandeep%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40imvangasandeep%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20making%20any%20assumptions%20Miss%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fikiranrao%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ikiranrao%3C%2Fa%3E%20!%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt's%20a%20fact%20reported%20by%20a%20very%20big%20media%20channel.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnArticle%20Link%20%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BC%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdLKVn5pPO4%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdLKVn5pPO4%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlJcLHmHwGJ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FlJcLHmHwGJ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Animal%20The%20Film%20(%40AnimalTheFilm)%2